About
=====

This is the rc.lua my main config script for the awesome wm

Features
========
autostart application with runonce,
integrated shutdown menu,
randowm wallpaper effect,
different layout setup for each tag,
split the rc.lua into single files
added some programms to the menu

Widgets
=======
Network usage widget,
Memory widget, in %
Acpitool based battery widget,
Cpu widget, in %

Requirements
============
xscreensaver
slock
acpitool
pm-utils
habak
Awsome version
==============
awesome v3.4.9 (Smack)
 - Build: Mar 26 2011 21:52:27 for x86_64 by gcc version 4.5.2 (rootman@virtualkitchen)
 - D-Bus support: x

Theme
=====
rootman
 - only modified some font colors & deactivated Wallpaper

Other Files
===========

Notes
====
rc.lua: The Failsafe load, try to load awesome.lua else load default config

Todo & Errors
=============
